{"type": "article", "id": 4177, "title": "Ottomatic 智能咖啡机", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-08T07:41:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052331211gIeWUObaX9z7EVt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t家居产品越来越智能这件事简直就是懒人的福音。正值严冬，赖床一族早起的困难程度可想而知，对于那些早起自己有煮咖啡的习惯的人，时间更是紧迫。日前，美国咖啡品牌 Chemex 就推出了一款能够帮你节省时间的智能咖啡机 Ottomatic 。早起睡眼惺忪时，你只要在咖啡壶铺上一层滤纸然后按下一键煮咖啡按钮，后续的工作 Ottomatic 就可以自动完成了。待你洗漱完毕，就已经能闻得见浓郁的咖啡香气了。定价 350 美元，<a href=\"http://www.chemexcoffeemaker.com/coffeemakers/ottomatic/ottomatic-coffeemaker.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233119UwGiabvthzD5FTOI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4109375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233120qtmGo5eO2yjRv1wd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4109375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233120fOJz7m2a4tr8iGe9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233120Fv3HJuZ0KiCrBX6q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.34375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}